At Prince BarberShop, we bring you nostalgia with a modern twist. From the authentic barber chairs, our old-fashioned hot lather and straightedge razor shaves to our relaxing head and neck massages,Prince BarberShop sets a new standard for barber shops. Whether you’re looking for a traditional short hair cut or a more contemporary men’s hairstyle, we invite you to visit one of our barbers and experience for yourself why Prince BarberShop is simply a cut above the rest!
